        {
            "title": "屯門公路辣跑自焚 女司機棄車逃生",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"消防到場救火。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/067d4c4ada4ff8bc3c940365535fe925/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041115273211631.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">消防到場救火。fb：馬路的事討論區</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（11日）午3時許，一輛林寶堅尼跑車沿屯門公路往九龍方向，途至哈羅國際學校對開時，跑車車尾突然冒煙起火，女司機把車停在避車處後棄車逃生，消防到場將火撲熄，初步懷疑機件故障肇事。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4189738/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救火。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6965736cbcf6627292cbdace6a877b1c/2025-04/01_0_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救火。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
